result.name: Veggie Express

reviews.text: Excellent place for vegan foreigners. Nice people willing to make you happy. Food is great and fresh. Not like the Three Virtues that is across the street. Here people are nice and the help you choose the right dish. Also you can order for tske away. I have been eating there for 5 days straight during a business trip.

This place has become my go to takeaway place to eat alone at home. Despite it doesn't serve meat, it is arguably the best local eatery in the area for its price range based on quality and flavour of dishes. Beware of long wait during dinner hours, best to reserve a table.
I'm not a vegetarian but a friend took me here and I was highly impressed! If I hadn't known I was in a vegetarian restaurant, I wouldn't have guessed (except the tomato chicken gave it away).
Loved the ee mee... Egg noodles with mushroom. Many other choices too.

Excellent lacto ovo vegetarian food with good variety, has allergen information for milk and eggs. Would recommend the stir fry rice cake with veggie chicken, the milk tea was also very yummy. Service bit rushed and prices are a bit pricey, but overall a good meal.

result.name: 聰嫂原素

reviews.text: 非常好👍👍🏻👍食物有高级餐廳水準😋😋😋很滿意💥🙏🙏🙏💥
少油少鹽👍
素食以新派菜及快餐店形式經營，有早餐，午餐，輕食及晚餐餐單，價錢俾素食館平宜，也不收加一，但繁忙時間經常要等位。

Excellent place for vegan foreigners. Nice people willing to make you happy. Food is great and fresh. Not like the Three Virtues that is across the street. Here people are nice and the help you choose the right dish. Also you can order for tske away. I have been eating there for 5 days straight during a business trip.

可惜午餐只跟熱飲，例湯要加錢。客人比較多，工作人員好忙。只收現金。

叫了飲品，再叫例湯，例湯要正價，好唔好飲見仁見智，其實都不錯，係貴咗少少。

午餐焗豬扒飯及全日早餐都好食的。

20190108
焗素豬飯，比以前更好食，汁輕身咗，更容易入口。連熱飲$50。

20190114
英式早餐，份量夠但相對輕盈，味道都可以，連熱飲$50。

20190129
都係焗豬

20190130
芝士白汁西蘭花素蝦丸焗飯，$50，叫做有兩件菜。

20190226
豉油王龍鬚炒麵，$50。
如果係金菇豉油王炒麵仲正。

20190319
味菜素牛柳絲炒麵，$50。
麵好脆，夠香口，豆豉好香，整體好食。

20190325
今日都係焗豬，無乜特別。
最特別就係我對面個食客，同我同一時間叫，佢叫素牛炒飯，結果我食完飲完，佢碟飯先到，好慘。

20190410
乾炒素牛河，$50，都不錯。

20190417
試新野，散叫星洲炒米，再加個半價湯，$61。都唔錯，咁樣叫個半價湯好似抵少少。
